   emission and Kalbach systematic angular distr.                 5128 1451
   (code PCROSS by R.Capote et al)                                5128 1451
 - Hybrid Monte Carlo preequilibrium model(M.Blann)               5128 1451
   (code DDHMS by M.Chadwick, mod. by B.V.Carlson)                5128 1451
 - Complete gamma-ray cascade after emission of                   5128 1451
   each particle, including realistic treatment of                5128 1451
   discrete transitions                                           5128 1451
 - Access to OM segment of the RIPL library [RIPL]                5128 1451
 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                5128 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               5128 1451
   and gamma strength functions based on the RIPL                 5128 1451
   library [RIPL]                                                 5128 1451
 - Automatic retrieval of experimental data from the              5128 1451
   EXFOR library                                                  5128 1451
 - ENDF-6 formatting (code EMPEND by A.Trkov)                     5128 1451
   coupled to graphical presentation capabilities                 5128 1451
   (code ZVView by V. Zerkin) through the chain of                5128 1451
   PrePro codes by D. Cullen                                      5128 1451
 - ENDF checking codes (CHECKR, FIZCON, PSYCHE)                   5128 1451
 - Highly automated fitting of optical model                      5128 1451
   parameters (by B.V. Carlson)                                   5128 1451
 - KALMAN code for fitting experimental data and                  5128 1451
 - generating covariances                                         5128 1451
 - Support for NJOY                                               5128 1451
